eric construction of involutive dyadic MDS matrices\nfrom Reed Solomon codes. Finally, we discuss the implementation aspects of\nthese dyadic MDS matrices in order to build efficient block ciphers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Feb 2014 08:48:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Mar 2014 18:12:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-06"}
